These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea
House: tower, cape-cod
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, singing
2 different pets are kept: cat, lizard
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: bellflower, balloon-flower
2 different games are played: mah-jongg, canasta
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, tram
1. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
2. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the owner of the cat##8
3. the person who's hobby is singing is not the person who growsbellflower##6
4. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the left of the owner of the lizard##5
5. the owner of the lizard is not to the left of the person driving the roller##8
6. the person playing canasta is not the person driving the roller##6
7. the tower house is the person who's hobby is board-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea   | coffee      |
| House          | cape-cod | tower   |
| Hobby         | singing    | board-games |
| Pet           | cat     | lizard    |
| Flower   | balloon-flower    | bellflower       |
| Game   | mah-jongg    | canasta        |
| Transport     | roller     | tram        |

